'''''Prank My Mom''''' is an American comedy television series on [[Lifetime (TV network)|Lifetime (TV Network)]]. The series debuted on September 27, 2012 and was hosted by [[Vivica A. Fox|Vivica A. Fox.]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.indiewire.com/2012/09/vivica-a-fox-to-host-lifetimes-all-new-hidden-camera-series-prank-my-mom-142219/|title=Vivica A. Fox To Host Lifetime’s All-New, Hidden Camera Series ‘Prank My Mom’ {{!}} IndieWire|last=Courtney|website=www.indiewire.com|language=en|access-date=2017-09-26}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://deadline.com/2012/09/prank-my-mom-new-series-lifetime-vivica-a-fox-329774/|title=Lifetime Picks Up Vivica A. Fox-Hosted 'Prank My Mom'|last=Team|first=The Deadline|date=2012-09-05|work=Deadline|access-date=2017-09-26|language=en-US}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.eurweb.com/2013/01/vivica-a-fox-is-single-and-working-on-a-new-show/|title=Vivica A. Fox is Single and Working on a New Show {{!}} EURweb|date=2013-01-27|work=EURweb|access-date=2017-09-26|language=en-US}}</ref><ref name=":0">{{Cite news|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/vivica-a-fox-lifetime-prank-my-mom-368146|title=Vivica A. Fox Tapped to Host Lifetime Hidden-Camera Series|work=The Hollywood Reporter|access-date=2017-09-26|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.eurweb.com/2012/09/vivica-a-fox-on-her-surprise-of-a-lifetime-watch-vivs-emotional-response/|title=Vivica A. Fox on Her Surprise of a Lifetime (Watch Viv's Emotional Response) {{!}} EURweb|date=2012-09-07|work=EURweb|access-date=2017-09-26|language=en-US}}</ref>

== Premise ==
The television series is a [[Lifetime (TV network)|Lifetime (TV Network)]] half-an-hour comedy show that provides centers around mothers being pranked by their children, by being unknowingly put in funny situations<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.nbcsandiego.com/entertainment/celebrity/Vivica_A__Fox_Talks__Prank_My_Mom__All__National_-173742371.html|title=Vivica A. Fox Talks "Prank My Mom"|work=NBC 7 San Diego|access-date=2017-09-26|language=en}}</ref>.<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.mylifetime.com/shows/prank-my-mom/about|title=About Prank My Mom {{!}} Lifetime|work=Lifetime|access-date=2017-09-26|language=en}}</ref>

